Description: terminal monitor for Claude Code token usage and analytics
 claude-code-usage-monitor provides a Rich-based terminal interface for
 monitoring Claude Code token/session usage in real time.
 .
 It includes usage aggregation, pricing calculations, session analytics,
 and trend views for developers who want direct visibility into AI usage.
